{"tid":565910,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【氣象】（2018年2月中旬末）新春快樂！受海洋氣流影響，農曆新年期間本港天氣和暖，潮濕有霧","createTime":"2018-02-19T12:25:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T16:15:08.000Z","uid":44630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5c511395f2b9643293443cd7794ae6a37072dac1","tid":565910,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:25:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: navy;\"><img src=\"http://imgur.com/fxgjJzQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FfxgjJzQ.png&h=e15d1b57&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>氣象討論：2018年2月中旬末</ins></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">此帖文討論期：2018年2月19日至21日</span></span></strong><br />\n【註】 氣象討論帖一般逢每月1日、11日及21日發出新帖文。　當新帖文發出後，或有颱風追擊帖發出，原有的氣象討論帖會隨即停用。　為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">氣象台專頁現已登場</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://x.co/FBlike\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FFBlike&h=5fdd3157&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://fb.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2FHKGweather&d=nVF4NZ7RNe9PlxsyqN9ZHhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=1da80fb1\" target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/HKGweather</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://x.co/TWlike\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FTWlike&h=e9b064ef&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://twitter.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKGweather&d=nVF4NZ7RNe9PlxsyqN9ZHhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=099af528\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/HKGweather</a></span></em><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/BZfpfrS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBZfpfrS.png&h=9df3da65&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://youtube.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2FHKGweather&d=nVF4NZ7RNe9PlxsyqN9ZHhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=a66bf5bf\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtube.com/HKGweather</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>◤參考網頁</ins></span></span><br />\n◆ 實時天氣照片：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/ts/index_webcam_uc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fts%2Findex_webcam_uc.htm&d=nVF4NZ7RNe9PlxsyqN9ZHhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=df983e71\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/ts/index_webcam_uc.htm</a><br />\n◆ 天氣雷達圖像：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/radars/radarc_range1.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fradars%2Fradarc_range1.htm&d=nVF4NZ7RNe9PlxsyqN9ZHhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=b236cb36\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/radars/radarc_range1.htm</a><br />\n◆ 機場天氣預報：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/aviat/taf_decode.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Faviat%2Ftaf_decode.htm&d=nVF4NZ7RNe9PlxsyqN9ZHhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=8c1b2bc1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/aviat/taf_decode.htm</a><br />\n◆ 認識天氣現象：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/education/edu01met_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Feducation%2Fedu01met_c.htm&d=nVF4NZ7RNe9PlxsyqN9ZHhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=15358742\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/education/edu01met_c.htm</a><br />\n◆ 各類天氣術語：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/flw_description/flw_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fcurrwx%2Fflw_description%2Fflw_c.htm&d=nVF4NZ7RNe9PlxsyqN9ZHhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=56f40aa1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/flw_description/flw_c.htm</a><br />\n◆ 各類警告定義：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/textonly/explain/introc.htm\