ZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 風向及風速／陣風／能見度<br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/2qmY2P8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2qmY2P8&h=dfc13b59&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/2pSAtuf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2pSAtuf&h=f73e8d68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/2pIOlLS\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2pIOlLS&h=ce3b8944&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 珠江口陣風及閃電定位／天氣雷達<br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/SuV1UB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2FSuV1UB&h=aa5b9639&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://j.mp/1mOf5kb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F1mOf5kb&h=f43ed746&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 地面天氣圖<br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/2a5ticH\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2a5ticH&h=b05f53f9&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://j.mp/2ahInaZ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2ahInaZ&h=2a1d8db0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/2ajChbn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2ajChbn&h=22f823b8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://j.mp/2ap2lTE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2ap2lTE&h=475ff2cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 衛星雲圖<br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/2a7TpCM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2a7TpCM&h=ef01e17d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://x.co/1Oc5V\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2F1Oc5V&h=2e7774ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/Meu94L\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2FMeu94L&h=e469b653&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://j.mp/pSSahs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2FpSSahs&h=61ae872d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 熱帶系統</strong></blockquote>"},{"pid":"fb29b0749c3bce8d5a7b527cee048a7902b98098","tid":565910,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:25:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/195920_a8eb65cd89e86366b8adbf9ac89d9381.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F195920_a8eb65cd89e86366b8adbf9ac89d9381.png&h=fae8adfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/195923_e99c938c30cd56e0bccaf84c7e4a6b39.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F195923_e99c938c30cd56e0bccaf84c7e4a6b39.png&h=60556b31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/195927_6b3db2a3d336e5e387ba5704a51812cb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F195927_6b3db2a3d336e5e387ba5704a51812cb.png&h=85440aef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/200632_7fe23404e4af61b17fb5eb78279ea69b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F200632_7fe23404e4af61b17fb5eb78279ea69b.png&h=27f79c49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馮瑞權-澳門氣象局前局長<br />\n風水權-馮瑞權俗稱<br />\n風水靜，神婆靜，作法靜，巫婆靜-現任澳門氣象局副局長梁嘉靜俗稱<br />\n赤的疑惑-高登氣象台台長<br />\n七長官/7長官-製作氣象台警報gif會員<br />\nRose-製作高登風格天氣警告圖的會員，其作品並不授予連登使用<br />\n楊振權副庭長-Baroclinic於高登的最新名字<br />\n桜の抹茶刺身-連登氣象post負責人1<br />\n道地檸檬綠茶-連登氣象post負責人2<br />\n雪菜肉絲炆米-連登颱風航空交通post負責人<br />\n夏天冬天夏天(#45439)-居於佐敦有一定氣象知識但擁有異常體感經常發表與氣溫相關煩膠言論的奇怪會員。<br />\n一個地球人-連登中仔細分析颱風走向的高質會員<br />\n李棟旭-連登中製作大量有趣的氣象post相關改圖的會員（包括以上四幅術語圖）<br />\n力場J-貼出李首富照片並提醒各巴絲記得準時返工的會員<br />\nDH-direct hit 本港一百公里內掠過<br />\n中出-風暴中心直接橫過本港<br />\n貓5- cat5 五級颱風的英文簡稱<br />\n五隻貓-同上，有cat1-5<br />\n醉警-酷熱天氣警告誤字<br />\n南海之王-氣象迷對香港天文台的尊稱，指其對南海熱帶氣旋預測表現良好，但只限接近廣東沿岸的南海部份，因此又被稱為南海北部之王<br />\nSTNR-滯留不動<br />\nN0.1-向北移0.1度，/E/S/W（東/南/西）同理<br />\n8中X-天文台指定8個測風站中有X個達標<br />\nlogin-登陸，源於cctvb錯將&Prime;登陸&Prime;打成&Prime;登錄&Prime;<br />\nlogin password-由上引申之術語，意指登陸地<br />\n近岸爆發-熱帶氣旋在靠近沿岸時急劇增強，令沿岸地區威脅大增<br />\n0號戒備/注意/留意訊號-香港傳媒於熱帶氣旋仍末形成時，已大肆吹奏香港會打風。此詞用於諷刺傳媒猶如代替天文台發出熱帶氣旋警告訊號<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/wcmdx6ns\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwcmdx6ns&h=b28e8ee5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上圖為一分鐘風速標準，轉化至十分鐘標準（hko,jma標準）請乘0.93<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nchan ho.jpg-副檔名可以改為任意三個不同英文字，為伊甸園市長愛用圖片，即下圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5684sbe3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5684sbe3&h=77a8e30f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下圖為兩登氣象台提及峴港時愛用cap圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/l01vgzfi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fl01vgzfi&h=215aae1f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"562d3c3c8133bb3bc1a803358719937cf93e54d3","tid":565910,"uid":71620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:30:01.000Z","msg":"D大褸羽絨可以收埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ff114abc8e0ef832ebc97c3cac8e5b77b5ee55","tid":565910,"uid":140834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"562d3c3c8133bb3bc1a803358719937cf93e54d3","tid":565910,"uid":71620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:30:01.000Z","msg":"D大褸羽絨可以收埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:39:58.000Z","msg":"香港人腥港人20度樓下都係羽絨"},{"pid":"c023048396bf23cd3372233bd096595a0051e47e","tid":565910,"uid":91897,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"96ff114abc8e0ef832ebc97c3cac8e5b77b5ee55","tid":565910,"uid":140834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"562d3c3c8133bb3bc1a803358719937cf93e54d3","tid":565910,"uid":71620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:30:01.000Z","msg":"D大褸羽絨可以收埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1