20/231907_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F231907_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2966d976&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉左溫吹襲南島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （新聞仍然報tc果陣既名Gita錯唔晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係由tc轉化而成既溫氣會保留原名，東北亞果d都會，不過因為通常都直衝太平洋唔再影響人，或者留係千島海域同其他溫氣合體，所以好少再提佢個舊名）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5153b51ebc43b5d985393b7cba3d52395667e5be","tid":565910,"uid":44630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T16:15:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\"><img src=\"http://imgur.com/fxgjJzQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FfxgjJzQ.png&h=e15d1b57&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">氣象討論</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">此帖文已停用，請在以下帖文集中討論：</span></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n【氣象】（2018年2月下旬）旬初東北季候風為本港帶來相當清涼的天氣，後期隨著季候風緩和，天氣回暖<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/567213\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/567213</a></strong>"}]}